* requirement
**database: mariadb
install: yum install mariadb mariadb-server
start server: systemctl start mariadb
config: mysql_secure_install
login: mysql -u root -p ****


** php
yum install php php-devel
yum install php-cli php-common php-mysql php-gd php-imap php-ldap php-odbc php-pear php-xml php-xmlrpc


** apache httpd
yum install httpd
systemctl start httpd



* install
download the wordpress and unpack it into /var/www/html



